name: ShipMyCar
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ship my car
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Whether you’re moving to a different part of the country or selling a car to someone far away, you’ll need to get a quote on the price of transporting your car, truck, van, or motorcycle for a long distance over the road. This unique Alexa skill allows you to get a shipping quote every day, providing you with the most up-to-date information available.

How much does it cost to ship my car door to door? To find out and instantly check out this Alexa Skill.

Our quotes calculator requires No Personal Information to get an estimate.

Thank you for using our service!
